unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of the Director of Student Affairs, University Heights
abstract_ssm: This collection is made up of the papers of the Office of the Director of Student Affairs at New York University's  University Heights campus from 1896 until 1973, when the campus closed. It includes records of various student organizations, events, and fraternities and sororities.
subject_ssm: Student newspapers and periodicals |z New York (State) |z New York.
Commencement ceremonies |z New York (State) |z New York |v Periodicals.
